Mongrethod Starting stats 7 Int, 1 Agi, 9 Str, base speed 320, base damage 6, Stats Gain per level 1.00 int, 1.30 str, 0.20 agi
Starting item Gaint Cleaver give 3 damage and 2% lifesteal base attack time 2.30 Auto-Attack,Tank,Mage

LEVEL 20 TALENT

Talent 1
increase Mongrethod health by 275 and his life regeneration by 3.5
Mongrethod will gain 25% of his health into bonus mana and every 100 current mana it will give Mongrethod 0.4 armor and 1% magic resist,
he also gain a 7 spell call Chaos Shield, all damage taken will be on Mongrethod mana instead of his health for 4 seconds, 60% of the
mana he lost will be gain back and also increasing his mana regeneration by 8.5 for 7 seconds after the shield duration ends, coldown of 
40 seconds

Talent 2
increase Mongrethod attack damage by 14 and his attack speed by 35
increase Mongrethod spell amp by 0.7% for every 8 current attack speed he got and increase his Rain of Fire Strenght scaling by 1% for
every 4 current attack damage he got, Rain of Fire will also gain 5% of Mongrethod health into bonus radius and will heal Mongrethod by
0.9% of his max health every time it damage enemys, Burn damage will give 0.1% health back.

PASSIVE D OR F PitLord
Increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF 
Mongrethod will gain 4 mana from strenght and 2 health from Inteillgence, he also gain 25% more Inteillgence and Strenght from items,
each Strenght and Inteillgence points will give Mongrethod 0.20 attack speed his spells will always spellvamp for 10% of the damage dealt
and each instence of damage the enemys take from his spells will reduce their healing Source by 1% up to 13% reduction for 8 seconds
that refresh on hit, he also start with a special ring.
DEBUFF
Mongrethod will lose 35% attack speed and each point of Agility will make Mongrethod lose 1.35 attack speed and 2 movespeed, he cannot
have more than 350 movespeed and slowing effect will last 75% longer and have 30% more slowing effect as well, every 0.4 seconds of 
slows duration will damage Mongrethod by 0.6% of his max health and also burn 1.4% of his max mana as well and 25% of that mana burn
will be damage.

UnderWorld Ring Special Item
increase spell amp by 6% increase by 0.4% every level
increase mana regeneration by 0.4 increase by 0.2 every level
increase life regeneration by 0.2 increase by 0.1 every level
can also be use to double the effect of the Ring for 10 second, cooldown of 110 second

talent level 40 upgrade PitLord
add a new modifier Chaos Lord
Mongrethod will gain 25% cooldown reduction and he also gain 0.7% spell amp for every 4 strenght he got, he will alway have 2 Chaos
Infernal aside him destroying everything in the name of there new lord Mongrethod, they will last until they die and will respawn every
75 seconds after they die.

GREATER CHAOS INFERNAL STATS
health 250 plus 40% of Mongrethod health
